Ano uru lau ta Jon ma la-uh au ala hamon. Eme Jises asehek i tiri lau ta nyala Jon, “Buku sah, aha mene ala kon lomale an, anya katou sasah? Ari bwidiu awa-is nyukunyok ereu bolo jor neh? Sebwe, bwe nadeh!
Ma ou badeh, basolou suluw bala batuk bwe, arile iy badeh, asolou suluw i kona katik.
Ano iy tiye i toro, “I deh, budon tado handru ndraheh?”
Ya iri lau badeh, aden hawe iri taya ndranyen. Eme Jises anya, “Aha kandru-uk, iy bamak bwe, iy badeh, amadin le oh.”
Tasah, buku none ari ndramak anya katawi kohan kudu, kohan kameh ano. Arile, buku none ari ndramak abudon jo ya kohan ano, iy kameh winiyan andrei kohan ja.
Eme Jemis uru Jon anuhun kandriyen doh badeh, eme uru ndremenya Jises, “Laban, ou aseken to kaloh jih udu kandrah keme andri kasulumwi iri?”
Na len doh badeh, Jises idih labai na sekesek ta Malawin Ndrabun, eme iy tiye, “Tama, ou Laban badu munyak ma kandrah! Jo masiye ou! Tasah, ou tone lakou dah ta mada iri lau ta tanan, ma hawe iri lau anya iri tanan labai, ya ou leheyani i tiri nah, tana iri lakou bwe. Ehe, idoh asahan na seken tam le.
Ma ou ame atondrok kon mari.
Jona badeh, i nyara kalem ta lau badu Ninibe na len bwena mene, ya jo Nadu Ndramak Awas ale, i nyara kalem ta lau na len dah.
Ado badeh, ndratana ado, iri lau asih sirih nadu bwisik ma limeh na luk bororoh saraman la-uh (2t) le, neh? Arile, tama ado badeh, atondrok sirih doh udu mwasin labai. Kindrei bamani iri ari se bwe.
ki buku none iri lohowan abe-en ndramak ta kati asiu udu ta molak eme hamon. Ya i buku none iy eme asumon, oro kameh sulu-i kou asak tan.
Eme iy tiye i ta ndramak ta atondrok anya, ‘Jaha taloh ai, jo eme anya katou kei pik dah, ta salin ya eme, jo se batou ari salin bwe. Kei pik kede-eh a-un gwa ta munyak laleyah, ya eme kamwetehei ki-iu!’
Na len ta amunyau ari, Jises aimon nyamon udu asiu ta tinan tiri Parasi ari. Eme iri badeh, atehei mada iri udu tan.
“O bwe em, ki buku none ari kabin kili kamekes bahun i ta kabin ari ja. Idah kameh iy manyah ma lomondra op, ‘Oro lau ta bahun tek ma 10,000 kada-ah winiyan adai oro lau ta bahun ta kabin ma 20,000 kodo-oh, deh bwe?’
Eme lohowan anya, ‘Nadu tinem mene badeh, ndrame hamon ja. Ya eme tamam badeh, idi bulumakau kasen i ta aimon tan, tasah iy badeh, bamak bwe, iy ma mwasin le ndrame hamon ja.’
“Ano, Lasarus imek ya iri angelo badu kandrah ame andrei iy ili manyah udu ka-u Abraham. Ano ndramak tan lakou solo-an ale imek, ya eme iri ahi iy.
Ano Jises tiye i toro lau tan anya, “Na len eme, ado kameh aseken labai ta atou ari len ta Nadu Ndramak Awas, arile ado kameh winiyan batou bwe.
Eme ale iri lau atiye nadu iri bwisik ame hawe Jises ya iy kedeu minen le ki bada iri, ta edeu nyosowan ki tiri. Eme oro lau ta Jises anyolom badeh, oro abolosen i tiri.
Jises ili bolo kon Jeriko. Iy edek san amwenen ta iu.
Ya, i buku none are lau kandremenya ah anya, ‘Ah anya katalou malou tan ta sasah?’ Ah katiye ki buku doh, ‘Laban gok udu tan.’”
Eme oro asehek nyala aliy udu ndrokowa oro ari ari anya, “Buku none to katiye anya, ‘Idoh lakou badu kandrah,’ idah kameh iy ndremenya to ja anya, ‘Buku sah ado batehei budon tado bala ta aliy bwe?’
Ano iy bwaneh sudi nyawe nadu tinen i tan, eme iy imek, ma nadun bwe le.
Ano iy tiye i toro ja anya: “Kon munyak tinan ari kameh amekes bahun i ta kon tinan ari; ya kabin badu kon rakon kameh amekes bahun i ta kabin badu kon rakon ja.
Eme iri lau tinan tiri pris, hawe iri lau ta leheya kandriyen tiri Juwis anya kadi Jises ki san ta bahana le. Tasah, iri badeh, anoh iri lau solo-an ado aliy.
Arile, Saimon, jo badeh, ndrasolom ta budon handru tam sataku. Ya, i buku none ou taku, ou badeh, tubuni ndrinem ma ou aseben budon toro kirih ja.”
Eme Pita anya, “Aden, jo bwe!”
Ya eme iy tiye i tiri anya, “Ado tiyani ndramak dah eme, ado anya iy badeh, amekes bolo ndrokowa iri lau andra-i. Udu mada ado nane ndra-au badeh, jo batakalahei ari lakou ndramak dah, amekes andra-i, i buku none ado mene asehek, bwe.
Ano iy tiye i ta Jises anya, “Jises, i buku none ou ame hamon, ma boto-on tam atondrok kon mari, ou samani jo.”
Arile, uru baseleyani se iy bwai.
Ano, iy amekes budon toro aleu na sahou ta Kindrei.
Iy anya, “Jo Alaija bwe.”
Pilip i buku le Enduru uru Pita. Oro ma taloh badeh, badu kon tinan ari iri aloh Betsaida.
Arile, iri bakohok bolo sahou tan bamwenen bwe. Jises asehek, iy amwenen badeh, i buku asiu tinan ta Kindrei.
Ano badeh, oro lau ta Jon ala asehek i tan, “Ndramak ta leheya, iy ndramak mene udu hawem, udu kapa gwa Jodan bilisiu loboho rai, ou mene asehek iy; na len dah badeh, iy inyu iri lau, idah iri lau alih le hawen ai.”
Tama ahi iri badeh, atudun nyara Kindrei udu bwele-e mandrei kodo-on. Arile aha Juwis asehek Jerusalem badeh, kon ta atudun nyara Kindrei.”
Iy ndramak ta kabin nane tikisiy labai. Iy eme asehek i ta Jises i buku doh, “Ndramak tinan, ou ame talu kala, bwe kameh naduk imek ai.”
“Handru labai, jo katiye tado: Are lau iy anuhun sahou tek ma iy atehei budon in ta iy nane suni jo eme, kohan handru kameh winiyan bano bwe, iy kameh ta udu le buku doh. Iy winiyan bala ta mada sahou bwe. Iy ndrasakalawi imek, ma iy akohok kohan handru.
Pilip asehek i ta Jises i buku doh: “Sihinek ta bun ma ndru la-uh badeh, winiyan basihinei jabi ramen winiyan bala boho ndramak ari, ari are kede-eh bwe!”
Buku jo ndrasehek taha, aha ndranyolom jo, arile aha batehei budon taha handru bame tek bwe le.
Arile aha rayah badeh, batehei budon taha bwe.” Jises ndratanan are lau iy batehei budon ba-en tan bwe. Iy i tanan udu ndra bada katin ta are lau handru kameh amekes sa-oh tan.
Buku sani ku-i nah mwan udu bolo len ta amunyau, taha tanan, kandriyen malen ta Moses bandra-i bwe. Taha kede-eh an hamon le ta kandriyen handru ta Moses. Ya buku sah ja aha abolosen eme tek ta jo bwidi ndramak ari amwenen ja udu bolo len ta amunyau?
Ano le badeh, iri lau marakon au ala hamon ala kon tiri amwenen.
Are lau iy nane suni jo eme dah iy udu hawek. Iy winiyan bamani jo bwe, tasah jo amekes iri lakou in hamon ta budon tan.”
Iri Juwis asehek i tan ja i buku doh, “Ou bala mirihik ta jaha ma lomonoh (50) bo-oh! I buku sah ja ou ndranyolom Abraham?”
Eme taman uru tinen asehek anya, “Iy ndrabadok, ma iy winiyan ta asehek sahou, aha kandremenya iy.”
Iy ndramak ibo gok ta akohok ndramas le, iy ndramak doh iy ta atondrok iri sipsip bwe, ma iri sipsip doh, tan bwe. Buku iy anyolom mwi badu lokei sakaliye eme ta aimon iri sipsip, iy kameh inoh, ma iy ruwani iri sipsip areu, iy kameh atobwak iu. Mwi eme ini iri, ma iri kameh atalan laleyah.
Ma iri lau solo-an labai adek ame hawen. Iri ame asehek i tan, “Jon badeh, bamekes ari lahou tinan ma kalem bwe; iri sahou marakon iy asehek nyala iy ndramak doh badeh, marakon amwenen le.”
Mariya anuhun le badeh, iy suri iy ere loken suwi suwi, ma iy edek ili hawe Jises.
Iri badeh, asilah Jises, iri ales ado bolo kowah ta asiu tinan ta Kindrei, iri ndremenya iri ari, ari i buku doh, “Saba budon taha handru? Sebwe iy winiyan bame ta nyamon tinan dah bwe nadeh?”
Oro ala hawe Pilip, iy badu kon Betsaida udu loboho Galili, oro ame tiye iy, “Ndramak tinan, aso anya katou Jises.”
Maha-an udu aliy ta are lau iy atehei konan eme tek, ma iy baso-ok sahou tek bwe, sahou le nane jo ndrasehek kameh edeu maha-an i tan na len hamon.
Jises anya, “Ou anyolom, jo kameh atehei jabi ramen ili bolo suw, ano kameh jo atehei ili nan, badeh, iy le ai.” Iy eme atehei jabi ramen ili bolo suw ano iy atehei ili na Judas Iskariyot nadu Saimon.
Seben doh, iy Malawin Ndrabun, iy eme ta asehek sahou handru ta Kindrei. Iri lau marakon badu kon munyak winiya bandrei iy bwe, tasah iri winiyan batou iy bwe, ma iri winiya bala tanan iy bwe. Arile aha le kameh tanan iy ai. Tasah iy in hawe aha, ma iy kameh udu hawe aha, udu le buku doh.
Jo winiyan baloh aha bonyo-ou ja bwai, tasah iri bonyo-ou bala tana iri ta saba lakou handru iri kabin amekes bwe. Akohok kon ta bonyo-ou eme jo aloh aha kawas tek le, tasah jo ndrasihidiy ndrawek taha iri lakou marakon mene jo anuhun eme ta tama.
“Se luwen bwe, aha kameh banyolom jo ja bwe. Ano sese luwen bwe ja, aha kameh anyolom jo ja.”
Len jo udu ndra hawe oro, jo atondrok oro udu mwasin labai, are bahandra boto-on ta nyaram, ou mene tondrohon jo. Jo turuki oro na aliy, eme oro mari are mwasin. Iy ari le toro kameh amai iu mara-ei. Idah kameh iri sahou marakon udu bolo buk ndrabun asahan eme lewan handru.
Kayapas mene edeu budon ma iy tiye tiri Juwis i buku doh, “Mwasin, ta ndramak ari le, iy kimek ta saluwe lau marakon. Ndra-in ta lau marakon amak laleyah.”
Iri lau ta bahun tabuwi bada malou bobodon i se buku none barak ma atehei ili batun. Ano iri atehei kolau ra-ei saraman lawe-en ili la-un.
Ano iy asehek ili ta lau tan nane, “Iy badih kede-eh tinem.” Eme udu ndra bada len doh badeh, iy lau ta Jises nane andrei tine Jises ili asiu hawen ma tondrokei iy.
Uru ndremenya Mariya i buku doh, “Badih den, ou aden ndranye sah?” Iy asumon, “Iri ndrandrei Laban tek ndra-au, jo bala tanan bwe, iri ndratehei iy ndrado heh handru.”
Saimon Pita eme ili ndron ja, aseben oro ta ariu kubwin irek ta ni eme amik. Udu bolo kubwin badeh, ni ma rinek lomonoh taloh (153), iri ni ndra badan le, arile kubwin batarah bwe.
