Arile, iri lau rayah suri iri badeh, andresei iy. Oro lau doh badeh, badu asiu ta atukum tiri Juwis, ya oro lau nane doh badu boho kamen iri aloh, “Kamen tiri salibah.”  Ya, iri lau doh badeh, iri Juwis badu kon tinan Aleksandriya ya kon tinan Sairini. Oro rayah ja badeh, oro Juwis badu kon munyak tinan Silisiya hawe badu bada kon munyak tinan Esiya atukum hawe oro ta tebelese hawe Stiben.
“Na len doh badeh, tine Moses atehei iy eme len. Iy badeh, konen mwasin labai ma Kindrei aseken iy handru. Udu bolo bun ma taloh badeh, atondrok iy udu le asiu ta taman.
“Iri tubu taha iri badeh, mene kuhi asiu balei ta Kindrei ma sahou handru tan udu bolon mirihik tiri, udu kon lomale an. Amekes doh mene in hamon ta boho Kindrei tiye i ta Moses, amekes in hamon ta malawin Moses ndranyolom.
Ya eme iri lau mari ma tinan ma bwisik badeh, atehei budon tiri i tan anya, “Iy ndramak dah badeh, iy Kindrei, ma boto-on tan ili labai.”
Eme ma ndramak tinan badu Itiyopiya ndremenya Pilip anya, “Abo, ou tiye tek, are propet handru asehek nyalan dah? Iy asehek iy le deh? Bwe-em iy asehek nyala ndramak ari ja?”
Eme iri are anuhun iy asehek sahou badeh, mani iri atur anya, “Kede-eh iy ndramak mene udu Jerusalem idi iri lau mene aloh i ta nyaran doh i buku iy asehek kede-eh! Ma iy kede-eh eme ta ateu iri lau kala hawe iri tinan tiri pris ma iri kala bolo kou ai.”
Koniliyus eme sihidi sahou mari ta angelo nane asehek i tan, ano i toro, ano iy tiye oro ala Jopa.
Arile, iy badeh, aseken lau mari badu kon munyak tinan labai, buku ndramak ari ari anoh iy, ma amekes kandriyen mwasin le.
Ano jo lomondrani sasah Laban mene tiye i buku doh, ‘Jon badeh alomwa ado na gwa, arile ado kameh anyu ado na Malawin Ndrabun.’
Eme iri anya, “Ou kede-eh budon tam ndra-au oh!” Bwai, iy asehek le ili anya, “Ado kanuhun jo. Ndrakan en! Iy asah udu manan kodo-oh.”
Iri lakou doh asahan udu bolo jaha ma hanek lomonoh (450).
Arile, Pol uru Banabas asehek sahou nyarahan labai i tiri anya, “Aru badeh, kasehek sahou ta Kindrei ki taha Juwis bwena op. Arile, aha badeh, baseken bwe, ma sahou taha badeh, leheya i buku, aha kameh winiyan bakohok manyah mwasin ta Kindrei ta udu le buku doh bwai. Eme ma aru kameh ruwani aha kon dah areu, ya, aru kameh ala aseben iri lau badu kon leheleh ai.
Ano Pol uru Banabas atehei lau mwasin kasahan batun ta atondrok iri lau ta Kindrei badu kon rakon rakon. Eme iri abeles iri ta aimon nyamon, ma amekes salom i toro ma atehei oro a mine Laban ta lahou iri atehei i kani oro ta amekes.
Arile, to atorou ki toro ma katandra-un toro saimon nyamon iri ndratehei ndra mine kindrei ta wendreya, iri amekes na sukumada kei; oro samekes kandriyen ndra-in ta karei; oro saimon oda iri lakou buku me ma bulumakau ndra udu ta aliy, ma sa-un ndraye iri ale.
Ya eme oro sakalawi kon Misiya ma adek ala andri ala kon tinan Trowas.
ta mwena tiri lulik anya, “Aru badeh, lau badu baha tondrok ma kandriyen ta Rom. Ya, i buku sah oro lau ta anuhun sahou doh bwale oro ma banuhun sahou taru bwe. Aru bamekes se ari lakou bandra-i bwe, arile iri ame adai aru udu mada lau mari. Ano oro akahei aru laleyah ame bolo kou dah. Ya, na dah oro anya katone aru ka-au ai? Winiyan bwe, handru en! Oro le kame katiye aru ka-au.”
Ma iy bandriliu ta se lakou badu mine lau katiye ki tan bwe. Tasah, iy le badeh, iy kati ndramak ta edeu koha taha, ma hawe sasah, sasah ja i ta lau mari.
Eme iri lelen iy ta iy kudu hawe iri luluwen sese kudu gwek, arile iy bwalen.
Eme iri lau ta budon handru mene ame tiye sahou ta tikisiy udu mada lau mari ta sasah ndra-in iri ndramekes.
Oro lau doh badeh, ala bwena ala Trowas abe-en aso.
Ma udu bolo lahou tek mari, jo ndraleheya aha ta san ta kandriyen ta amekes gok boto-on, aha kaseben iri lau nyamu iri bwe. Ma taha kabudon sahou mene Jises asehek i buku doh, ‘Are ndramak, iy edeu lakou ili tare lau, iy badeh, sekesek tinan handru. Ma sekesek ta iy ndramak nane akohok lakou winiyan basakalawi sekesek ta iy ndramak nane aseben iy bwe.’”
Ahi ndratorowenei la-ukei ramen, ma ndratiyaniy ndrala tiri lau ta Kindrei badu leheleh, ma ahi tiye tiri i buku doh, ‘Aha saimon nyamon ala ndrala ta salom tiri kindrei nane iri asehek na sukumada kei. Ma aha saimon oda iri katin haka ndra udu ta aliy, ma hawe sa-un ndraye iri. Ma aha samekes kandriyen ndra-in ta karei.’”
Ma ou kameh a buku bohon ta tiye tiri lau mari ta saba lakou nane ou ndranyolom, ma ou ndranuhun.
Na mandraben ari ja badeh, iri lau rayah badu Juwis atukum ja, ta amekes sahou tandrakan ta adai Pol. Iri badeh, abeles iri winiyan bakohok nyamon, ma gwa bwe, winiya le iri kandrei batu Pol ki-iu labai.
6-8 Ou anuhun, iy ale none ta akohok iri kandriyen ndra-in solo-an eme bolo asiu tinan ta Kindrei. Arile, na bolo len doh badeh, ahi tawi iy.  Buku ou ndremenya iy ndramak kede-eh, ou amwenen kameh winiyan silahei iri lakou marakon nane ahi anya kadeu iy kili ta mada sahou ta aliy.”
Pol anya, “Bwai, jo ndrales ndrare ta sahou mada Sisa kada-ah kabwai, iy kabin ta atondrok kon tataha Rom. Aha winiyan atehei jo i ta sahou udu bolo asiu ta sahou le dah. Ya, ou ndratanam, jo badeh, bamekes ari ndra-in bala bada iri Juwis kede-eh, bwe-en.
Ma len solo-an badeh, jo iu ili bolo asiu ta atukum tiri Juwis, ma jo abwiyeh iri lau ta Jises doh. Ma jo atehei sahou ili ta lau rayah ta a-um iri, ma nohowa iri ta iri kabobose Kindrei. Eme ma ndrinek ibolosen labai, ma jo in hamon tiri ili, ili bolo iri kon udu len labai ta Jerusalem.
Iri lau badu ndron badeh, boto-on, ma ahi atas Krit le ai. Ma ahi ame asahan kon ari, iri aloh Salan Korohan, bado len ta kon tinan Laseya bwe.
Kane ahi lau marakon are bolo ndron nane doh i se badeh, ma lunek ndro tonoh onoh (276).
Arile, nadah, ahi anya kanuhun budon tam le amwenen, tasah ahi tanan, bolo kon mara-ei iri lau amekes sahou ta bobose ili ta lakou nane ha-un asahan bolo taha Juwis kede-eh.”
Ya eme kabatana Kindrei mesekei munyak eme taku dah, iri lau anyolom iri lakou iy ndramesekei. Na iri lakou le doh, iri lau winiyan atanan kandriyen rayah ta Kindrei. Handru, iri kandriyen doh amai ta mada iri, arile iri winiyan atanan ta iy badeh, udu kede-eh handru, ma boto-on tan ta udu le buku doh. Eme ma, ta katin doh, iy mesekei iri lau winiyan bawasai anya iri tanan iy bwe.
Ou badeh, anya ou ndra ari ai, ta atudun Kindrei, tasah ou badeh, Juwis, ma ou tanam batanau malen mari.
