Na len ou anyolom bohon i bwena ta lakou Jises kameh edeu tam badeh, ou sekesek. Buku none maha ma isi katok tam, ou sanunu-uh ma ou ado le. Ma, na len mari, ou amekes salom ma ou ado le ta salom; ou sabudon anya Kindrei kameh winiyan bamesekei bwe, ndri-iy.
Ma eme taha katondrok tekedek tataha kudu mwasin i buku none lau manyah ado bolo an na len; sala buku none taha ka-un gwa boto-on ma bwidi batu taha asahan lolo-ou, ya taha asehek sahou laleyah, ma amekes karei ma madasarah, ma samekes bahun hawe samekes madalakis sala ta ndramak ari ari, ndri-iy.
Eme ya jo aseken taha ari ari kamekes kandriyen mwasin ta seben ki ta nadu tine taha oro ari ari badu mirihik tataha, ta sasah le winiyan sebenei iy abadok ta budon mwasin.
Idah kameh oro anyolom iy,
Ma hawe sahou sekesek tek ki ta borobwar tek Persis. Iy badeh, badih ari ja amekes lahou solo-an solo-an ta Laban.
Jo edeu wurah i ta Kindrei ta jo banyu aha solo-an bwe. Jo anyuwi Krisipus uru Gayus le.
“Lakou mada taha banyolom bwe, ma ndranye taha banuhun bwe, ma basahan ta budon ta lau bwe le, iri lakou mwasin le badeh, Kindrei ndralokowaniy, tiri lau le aso-ok iy handru.”
Kora-on ari ndramak kawendreyani iy le amwenen. Buku ari mwan o badih udu bolo aha, iy in hamon ta kandriyen ta munyak dah, eme ma iy atehei budon tan i buku doh, “Tanan tek tinan labai, ma jo ere bwele-en labai tiri lau ta Kindrei rayah ja.” Mwasin ta iy katehei konan kili ta tanan badu munyak op, ma iy kameh winiyan asahan ndramak ta tanan ta kandriyen handru ta Kindrei.
Jo ndramak amwenen bado hawe aha bwe, arile malawik mwasin ma iri budon tek marakon badeh, udu hawe aha, i buku jo amwenen udu hawe aha. Jo ndranyulumwi iy ndramak ta karei nane ndrano, eme ma jo ndratehei iy ndrala ta sahou.
Aha ka ndra len ta iri kandriyen ndra-in ta karei. Iri kandriyen ndra-in rayah taha lau amekes, idoh bamekes bada taha bala bolo ko-ak bwe. Arile, buku ndramak amekes karei, iy ndrabwidi badan mara-ei ndrala bolo ko-ak.
Buku ou ndratasou, ou sasilah madasan ta atikah badih iu ja. Buku ou batasou bwe, ou sasilah iri madasan ta atasou.
Jo ndranyolom Laban tataha. Jo amekes gok ta Laban, eme ma aha asahan lau ta Kindrei ta gok nane jo amekes dah.
Aha nadu tine, jo aso-ok aha kabudon ki-iu kili hamon ta lakou marakon mene asahan ta tubu taha iri Isra-el. Udu bolo len ta Moses bwena mene, tubu taha iri marakon badeh, ado bahandra asi kandrah mene Kindrei atehei ta korohani iri. Ma iri adek bolo ndras aloh Retsi iri apou ala bilisiu.
Jo basehek bawek taha anya aha amwenen kameh amekes andra-i, bwe. Jo asehek ta iy ndramak ari ja kameh atona i buku aha ndrabwidiy ndrandra-i. Arile, i buku ari ndramak bamekes iri sahou buku doh bwe, jo winiyan ta aimon iri saba lakou jo aso-ok. Ya, tasah handru jo ki-in le hamon ta budon ta ndramak ari ja, ta saba lakou iy anya jo kabeleben ta amekes?
Ma, iy edeu wurah i ta Kindrei, ano iy abo-os jabi ramen doh i bwisik bwisik, ma iy asehek sahou ili toro lau tan i buku doh, “Idah odak amwenen. Jo edeu ta aseben ado. Ado kamekes kandriyen ki buku doh ta abudon jo.”
I buku badam ki sese le, ya badam handru kameh udu heh?
Arile, buku ou asehek sahou boho Kindrei, ou asehek amwenen ili tiri lau. Iri sahou tam nane doh atadau budon tiri abadok, sekeyani iri ta amekes kandriyen mwasin, ma amekes ndrine iri udu mwasin labai.
Handru, aha winiyan a-en hamon ta kandriyen jo ndrasehek taha. Tasah, iri propet ta Kindrei handru badeh, atondrok malawi iri ma boho iri amwenen, buku iri anya kasehek sahou.
I buku doh: Iri lau mwan ma badih bwena mene ahis hawe Adam, iri marakon badeh ndramak. I buku le, iri lau mwan ma badih ahis handru hawe Krais, iri kameh amak ame awas ja, ma akohok koha iri mwasin.
Koha kon munyak badeh, asahan bwena handru. Arile, koha Malawin Mwasin asahan hamon, ma iy udu bwele-en labai ja.
Stepanas uru Potunatus hawe Akaikus oro ma taloh mene ame hawek. Eme bwidi jo sekesek labai ta anyolom oro, tasah aha marakon winiyan bame dah banyolom jo bwe. Oro ma taloh nane doh akohok ndrahune aha ta amekes gok doh ta aseben jo.
Eme ma, jo ndraruwi ndrinek. Jo abudon i buku doh: Jo winiyan bala Korin ja, ma amekes maha-an ili tiri ja bwe.
Budon ma ndrine iri lau Isra-el bwena ndrahis, ma iri bala tanan moson o kati batanau doh, Moses mene edeu ili tiri bwe. Ma na dah ale, iri lau Isra-el, iri bala tanan moso kati sahou batanau bwe. Buku iri atehei budon tiri handru in ta Krais, Kindrei kameh winiyan sihi budon tiri, ma iri winiyan atanan handru ta kati moson ta sahou batanau.
Kindrei le ari badeh, ndralokowani taha ta akohok koha taha ha-un doh. Ma iy ndratehei Malawin Ndrabun ndrame tataha. Handru labai, Malawin Ndrabun, iy i buku sahou tandrakan ta Kindrei, ta iy kameh edeu iri lakou hamon, iy mene tiye ta edeu eme ta taha.
Ahi batone ndrine ahi taha bwe. Ahi badeh, aso-ok aha tinan labai. Aha amwenen badeh, tone ndrine aha, ma taha bado mwasin bwe.
Aha nadu tine aso i san ta Krais. Aso anya katiye tanan ta kandriyen mwasin ma tikisiy, Kindrei mene edeu ili tiri lau tan, mwan ma badih, are bada kon Masadoniya.
Eme ma, aha ari, ari kabudon ndrinem le amwenen op, ma ou tanam ta saba lakou, aha anya kadeu. Kora-on ari mwan o badih, ndrinen basekesek ta edeu lakou bwe, ma iy abudon i buku doh: “Iri mwan ma badih abadok labai ma aruwi jo, ma bwilik ama buku jo badeu rayah luk bwe.” Kora-on iri budon solo-an doh udu taha, ma aha adeu luk. Kindrei badeh, aso-ok ndramak, iy sekesek ma edeu lakou na so-ok ma na budon tan amwenen.
Tasah, jo abudon solo-an ta tekedek taha, i buku Kindrei abudon boto-on labai tiri lau mwan ma badih tan, kora-on iri katelei san mwasin. Jo aso-ok aha ka-en hamon handru ta Jises Krais le ari. Jo anya katehei aha kala mine Krais, buku tama badih bihin atik nadun anya kili bahandra mwan tan. Jo aso-ok
Ma Kindrei badeh, tama Laban Jises, iy le ari tanan, jo bawendreya bwe. Taha katudun nyaran kudu bolo len mara-ei!
Ma, ahi asalom ili ta Kindrei, ta iy kaseben aha, ma aha samekes ari kandriyen ndra-in. Jo amekes sahou dah ta Kindrei winiya leheya aha, ahi aposel handru. Ahi aso-ok aha kameh kamekes le kandriyen mwasin; iri lau abudon ahi aposel handru o bwe.
Eme ma, iri sekesek ma atudun nyara Kindrei. Tasah, jo badeh, ndra-en hamon ta Jises.
Sahou ta Kindrei badeh, ndrasehek ndra bwena, ta iy kameh aloh iri lau badu leheleh mwasin mara-ei ta madan i san ta budon handru le. Eme ma iy ndrasehek ndra ta Abraham ta sahou mwasin ta Krais i buku doh,
Ya, kandriyen tataha ari badeh, i buku sahou sokek ta amekes moso sahou jo atorou dah kaleu kamwenen. Buku ndramak ari munyak tan ranah laba tinan udu aliy, ya, buku iy ndramak doh, nadun mwan ari udu aliy. Nadun amwenen badeh, ibo gok udu bwele-e munyak doh, luluwen labai i buku ari bonyo-ou. Udu hamon, buku taman anyolom nadun ndrasahan awas handru, iy kameh winiyan tiye nadun ta atondrok munyak tan doh.
Tasah, badih udun ruwani iy kameh nadun i sola,
kandriyen ta ou amekes ou batudun ou bwe, ma hawe kandriyen ta budon tam winiyan bandra-i bwe. Ya eme ari batanau malen winiyan baturuki iri kandriyen doh bwe.
Kindrei bwetenei ndra bwena ta lakou iy anya kamekes ta gok ta Krais. Iy in hamon ta budon tan amwenen, ma iy leheya taha ta lakou tan doh, bwena mene aton mara-ei.
Ehe, Krais imek udu bada kei tondreh, ma ta gok doh, iy ndrasani kandriyen ta adai lau laleyah udu ndrokowa iri mwan ma badih badu Isra-el amwenen, ma iri mwan ma badih badu kon leheleh, kasahan rabuk le. Eme ma, iy ndradai kandriyen ta bahun laleyah ndra-au.
Malawin Ndrabun aseben taha ado mwasin, ma lakou doh iy amekes, i buku malou tabuwi taha ahis are le se. Eme ma aha kabadok ta ateu lakou doh kihis.
Aha samekes ndrine Malawin Ndrabun ta Kindrei sandra-i, ta kandriyen aha a-en hamon ta aliy. Aha kabudon kamwenen. Kindrei ndratehei Malawin Ndrabun buku kalem ndrawek taha ta aha katondrok len ta Kindrei eme akohok taha ame hamon ja.
Tasah, iy anya kamekes iri mwan ma badih ta Kindrei kasahan mwasin handru ta madan, ma iri kameh ari ndraka-an, ma ari bakuwa, ma iri lakou buku doh bwe. Iri kameh asahan lau ta Kindrei, ma ari ndra-in bwe.
Jo ndramak ta atiye sahou mwasin dah, ma ta idah le jo ili udu bolo asiu lulik. Kindrei atehei jo, ma jo amekes gok ta atiye sahou tan. Eme ma, aha kasolom kili ta Kindrei, ta jo kameh winiyan banoh ta atiye sahou mwasin dah bwe.
Ya eme i san ta jo udu hawe ado badeh, ma eme ya sekesek tado i ta Krais Jises ki tinan handru.
Eme ya ado kasekesek hawek ta aliy.
Eme ya ado nadu tine badu hawek i san ta budon handru, ado ka-en le hamon ta kandriyen tek, ma ado ale ka-en hamon ta kandriyen toro lau mene na len aso ado hawe ado.
Udu bolo salom taru na len marakon badeh, aru asolom aha ma adeu wurah i ta Kindrei, iy tama Laban tataha Jises Krais.
6-7 Aha ndranuhun sahou mwasin ta Laban Krais Jises, ma aha ndratehei budon taha handru ndrala tan. Eme ma, aha badeh, kahis hawe Krais, ma kadek na kandriyen tan. Aha badeh, kahis badan, buku kei ateh ma kandron ateu iy boto-on labai udu bwele-e munyak, ma buku asiu ales udu bwele-e ndru boto-on. Ma aha badeh, atehei budon taha boto-on labai in ta sahou mwasin doh, iri lau mene ndraleheyani aha ta aliy, ma len marakon aha kadeu wurah kili ta Kindrei ta iri lakou mwasin iy ndrabwidiy ndrawek taha.
Kandriyen ta aso-ok iri mwan ma badih badeh, ere bwele-en labai mara-ei ja tiri kandriyen rayah ja mene ndrasehek ndrawek taha. Ma iy badeh, atehei iri kandriyen mwasin marakon ili le winiyan, ma iy tawi ndrine aha mari i le se.
Jo Pol, jo atorou la-ukei dah. Sailas uru Timoti badeh, are hawek ale. Eme ma, aso ma taloh atehei la-ukei ramen dah ewek taha lau mwan ma badih ta Kindrei are bolo kon tinan Tesalonaika. Aha lau mwan ma badih ta tama taha Kindrei, aso aso-ok Kindrei hawe Laban Jises Krais, uru katikisi aha, ma ndrine aha kudu mwasin.
Handru, aha le amwenen badeh, a buku nyara aso tinan ma sekesek taso. Eme ma aso anya kawek hamon ta anyolom mada aha ja, ma kasekesek hawe aha marakon.
Ano, taha mwan ma badih nane bamak bwe le, ado kon munyak dah, Laban kameh akohok taha ala bolo asi kandrah hawe iri mwan ma badih nane, ma taha atukum hawe Laban. Eme ma, taha mara-ei kameh are hawe Laban ta are le buku doh.
Jo Pol, jo atorou la-ukei dah. Sailas uru Timoti badeh, are hawek ale. Eme ma, aso ma taloh atehei la-ukei ramen dah ewek taha lau mwan ma badih ta Kindrei are bolo kon tinan Tesalonaika.
Ma aha ale, kasolom kili ta Kindrei, iy kandrei aso are mine iri lau ndra-in kame len; iri badeh, ta amekes kandriyen ndra-in. Tasah, aha tanan, lau solo-an labai badeh, batehei budon tiri handru bala ta Kindrei bwe, ma iri baso-ok gok aso amekes dah bwe.
Tikisiy ta Laban i tataha badeh, amou handru eme bwele-ek, eme jo atehei budon tek handru i ta Krais Jises, ma jo atehei ndrinek mari i tan. Ya taha are lau ahas hawe Krais badeh, kandriyen doh, kudu tataha.
Oro katawi sahou handru mene Kindrei tiye ta budon handru ma budon toro kaleu kudu mwasin.
Balem ki tam kamwenen ma balem ki ta sahou ou leheya. Ou saruwaniy labai; tasah lakou ou amekes badeh, winiyan sebenei koha iri are anuhun sahou, ma winiyan sebenei ou ale.
Budon tiri lohowan mari badeh, iri kamekes ki ta lau ta atondrok iri badeh, ki buku doh: Saba lahou ndramak ta atondrok iri katiye iri kamekes badeh, ndra iri kamekes le, tasah kandriyen doh badeh, mwasin. Ya, ki buku none iri katebelese, badeh kameh, iri lau kameh bobose nyara Kindrei, ma hawe leheya ta to ale.
Kindrei ndratondrohani jo asahan aposel ma ndramak ta leheya. Tasah, iy aso-ok jo kamekes gok ta atiye sahou mwasin dah.
Bohom sala tiri sahou ndra-in, ari moson bwe. Tasah, iri sahou doh, iri lau amekes ta ariu lau a sola ala le san ta adeu kona iri ili ta Kindrei.
Na san doh, Kindrei lowosani iri lohowan tan, kamekes iri gok mwasin.
Eme ya, ndramak ta atondrok iri lau ta Kindrei, hawe ta ateu lahou ta Kindrei badeh, kandriyen tan kudu mwasin, ta iri lau badeh sasehek iy. Ma iy badeh, sabudon anya, iy ndra ari ai. Ma iy badeh, sala ndramak ta ndrinen ato-ou suwi ta losen, ma hawe iy badeh, sala ndramak ta a-un gwa boto-on solo-an. Ma hawe iy sala ndramak ta akeh lim suwi, ma hawe iy sala ndramak ta ndrakok.
Eme jo katiye kaleu ki tado ta sahou jo asehek dah: Kindrei badeh, tiye Jises Krais, ndramak ta akohok to ado bolo kandriyen ta karei ma lomondra ndra-in ame hamon, ma suni Malawin Ndrabun eme la-u to. Eme ta katin doh, Kindrei le mesekei Malawin Ndrabun tan amekes lahou boto-on udu bolo to.
Jo atehei budon tek boto-on handru, ta ou kameh a-en hamon ta sahou tek. Eme ma jo atorou la-ukei dah ewek tam. Ma jo ale ndratanan kandriyen ou amekes kameh udu bwele-en labai ja ta kandriyen nane jo ndratiye tam ta amekes, ma kameh asahan mwasin labai mara-ei.
“Ou ame manyah ado loboho minek salin, winiya jo le baratehei iri lau ta amekes budon ndra-in i tam barado bahandra katim.”
Kindrei ndratehei gok doh ndrala tan, ma iy in hamon ta sahou handru ta Kindrei ta iri kandriyen i buku le ta Moses bwena mene amekes udu asiu ta Kindrei.
Idoh ta leheya taha. Iri lau ma bwena mene anuhun sahou mwasin, arile iri bandrei amunyau doh bwe, tasah iri batehei budon tiri bala tan bwe. Arile, na dah, lau winiyan akohok amunyau doh kahis.
Ta idoh, taha sasehek ja ta iri leheya mwasin taha ndrakohok ma bwena mene ta nyala Krais. Arile, na dah taha kala ta leheya tiri lau-en le ai. Taha sala hamon ja tiri lakou mene taha ndrakohok tanan tiri. Iri lakou doh: ta mani kandriyen ndra-in ili san ta imek; ma ta atehei budon in ta Kindrei;
Libai basahan bwe le badeh, Melkisedek ndruni Abraham udu san, arile iy udu ndra bolo oda tubun Abraham kahis, udu bada len Abraham edeu iri lakou rayah ili ta Melkisedek. Eme ma idoh leheya taha ta Melkisedek badeh, pris randrah labai ja, ma iy udu bwele-en labai ja tiri pris badu boho kamen ta Libai.
“Jo Laban asehek, len eme kameh, jo amekes sahou randra le ha-un hawe iri lau badu Isra-el ma iri Juda.
I buku le ma mwena mene, Moses toboroya ndra ili bwele-e asiu balei ta Kindrei, ma ili bwele-e iri lakou marakon nane iri akohok ta atudun nyara Kindrei na aliy.
Malawin Ndrabun tiye ja:
Budon ta tubu taha iri handru in le ta Kindrei, eme ma bwidi iy sekesek tinan labai.
Rahap, iy badih ari ta bada belei, arile iy atehei budon tan boto-on handru in ta Kindrei, iy eme aseben uru lau la-uh badu Isra-el mene ala anya kanyolom saba lakou handru udu bolo kon Jeriko. Eme ma iy bamak bwe, bala buku iri lau nane banuhun boho Kindrei bwe.
Len ta taha ame hawe Kindrei, lakou asahan tataha bala buku asahan tiri lau badu Isra-el bwe, iri mene ala mirihik ta mandrei aloh Sainai. Iri ame ado mirihik ta mandrei doh, iri winiyan anuhun ma atona iri lakou mari doh handru. Eme ma iri anyolom jih taladan ili loken, ma lulik hutu-un tinan labai, ma jor atohou a tinan.
Tinan tiri pris amekes gok udu bolo asiu balei ta Kindrei, iy andrei ndraye sipsip ma bulumakau, eme iy tiyani ndra nane doh ili bolo asiu ndrok ndrabun ndrabun labai ta amekes salom ta talou kandriyen ndra-in tiri iu. Arile, sali iri sipsip ma bulumakau nane doh badeh, iri sulumwiy andrakak iu udu ndra manan, bado bolo kon bwe.
Iri lakou hawe ndramas mwasin labai mari badeh, marakon badu kandrah eme andri. Ya, tama taha Kindrei badeh, mesekei lomadan marakon badu kandrah, iy le amwenen badeh, suni iri lakou marakon mwasin doh eme andri tataha. Iy badeh, mwasin labai ma iy batobolowe kandriyen tan bala bame bwe, buku ari lakou, an bwidi malawi iri asahan, an anya ya tobolowe malawi iri lakou a lawe ano a mo-on ja. Arile Kindrei badeh, batobolowe iy bala bame bwe, iy ta udu le buku doh.
Aha nadu tine mwan ma badih ta Kindrei, buku ari taha anya, “Jo atehei budon tek mara-ei badeh, in le ta Jises Krais,” arile iy badeh, bamekes kandriyen mwasin ma ba-en hamon ta budon handru bwe, eme budon handru ta i ndramak doh badeh, ari moson bwe. Sebwe iri budon handru buku doh badeh, winiyan basebenei ndramak ales udu mada sahou ta Kindrei hamon kameh eme bwe.
Aha kanuhun! Are lau ale ta lomondra ndra-in ma ta ndrakok udu tiri, iri lau doh badeh, ta amekes lakou laleyah ma ta amekes kandriyen ndra-in.
Aha nadu tine, aha kabudon oro propet bwena mene, oro mene atiye sahou ta nyara Laban. Kandriyen tiri badeh, mwasin labai ta aseben taha. Iri lau ta kaliu badeh, banuhun sahou toro bwe, ma iri amekes kandriyen ndra-in i toro propet doh. Arile, oro atehei ndrine oro udu mwasin ta bwese iri maha-an. Aha badeh, kandrei kandriyen toro doh, ma ka-en hamon ta aliy.
Ehe, aha katondrok aha kamwenen, ma ka-en hamon ta kandriyen mwasin. Tasah, bwena mene aha a-en hamon ta iri kandriyen ndra-in, aha mene akohok ta tubu aha iri, arile na dah, aha ndratana aha, Kindrei ndrakonohei ma ndrakuhi aha ndrame len ta kandriyen badu bwena. Iy bakonohei aha bame hamon na bek nyikilikin hawe silba bwe. Iri lakou doh, lau badu kon munyak abudon tinan labai. Arile, gol hawe silba badeh, lakou badu kon munyak le. Hamon kameh iri amai au laleyah.
Aha kabeleben iri lau mari, ma aha kaso-ok iri lau atehei budon tiri handru in ta Kindrei. Aha kanoh Kindrei, ma kabeleben iri kabin badu kon munyak ale.
Iri su-u doh badeh, malawi iri lau ndra-in bwena mene iri banuhun sahou ta Kindrei bwe, kala Nowa mene amekes ndron tinan. Iri lau solo-an bala bolo ndron bwe, oro lau ma ndru la-uh le, ala bolo ndron nane doh. Oro bamak bwe, tasah gwa eme sebenei oro, bwese-ei ndron, ma ndron telebek. Arile, iri lau mari mene areu manan, amak an bolo wadah tinan.
Kindrei badeh, abudon ma aso-ok aha, ma iy atondrok aha ale. Eme ma, aha katehei maha-an taha mari kili le minen, ya iy winiyan mesekei lakou mari asahan amwenen ja.
Arile idah kameh, i buku le bwena mene ndra-au, iri propet ta wasai mene are ndrokowa iri Isra-el kameh, iri lau ta leheya tanan ta wasai asahan ndrokowa ado i buku le aliy. Iri lau ta leheya tanan ta wasai doh kameh leheya ado na tanan handru bwe, ya idah kameh, ado winiyan baseleyaniy bwe. Iri kameh sekere-ei lau a len ta Kindrei i buku ndramak atehei budon tan handru i ta aliy. Ma idah kameh, iri bisini lahou ta Jises Krais, ndramak handru ta akunoh iri ta karei ma lomondra ndra-in. Ya eme, na boho iri le doh, kameh tiyani ndra-in atok tiri, ma idah kameh, se nawin bwe iri akohok andra-i labai.
Ano, udu hamon ja, munyak mene atuh na gwa le doh, ma munyak andra-i, eme ma, bolo kon mari bala buku bwena mene ja, bwe.
Arile, jo badeh, atorou batanau ha-un ewek taha; ma aha anyolom moson ta aliy badeh, udu tan ma aha ale, tasah lulik anya ki-iu ai, ya lomada sun handru ndranya.
Jo atorou iri sahou dah ewek taha, ta asehek nyala aha, ta mada aha kaleu, kora-on iri lau ta wasai kawendreyani aha.
Aha naduk ta Kindrei, Kindrei le tondrokei koha aha, eme ma aha ndrasakalawi iri lau mwan ma badih ta asehek sahou wasai, tasah Malawin Ndrabun badeh, ereu hawe aha. Iy badeh sakalawi malawi lakou ndra-in ereu hawe iri lau ta wasai badu kon munyak dah.
Are lau ihis hawe Nadu Kindrei, iy ndrakohok kohan mwasin ale winiyan bano bwe. Arile, are lau bahis hawe Nadu Kindrei bwe, iy winiyan bakohok kohan mwasin ta ereu le buku doh, bwe.
Eme ma, taha lau ta Kindrei badeh, kaseben iri lau buku doh. Na kandriyen le doh, taha marakon kameh amekes gok i se ta atiye sahou handru ta Kindrei.
Lau rayah ta bolowa sahou ta Kindrei ndra-au laleyah badeh, mesekei budon tiri lau rayah taku. Eme ma, jo aso-ok aha kanone ta ariu budon hawe ndrine iri keme hamon ta sahou handru, i buku aha aruwi kei suwi suwi udu bolo jih eme len ma sandrakak. Aha kamekes kandriyen ta tikisiy kili tiri mwan ma badih nane a-en hamon ta kandriyen badu lulik. Iri amekes iri lakou doh, i buku awin ndra ndraka-an mara-ei. Aha kare ndra len tiri kandriyen doh, ma aha sa-en hamon ta aliy.
Ma jo atou ndramak ari, ya konen badeh,
Iy ndramak doh tiye jo ja i buku doh, “Ou atorou rayah sahou kili ta angelo ere bwena tiri lau ta Kindrei are kon Tayataira. Sahou i buku doh:
Ya, buku are lau ndranyen udu aliy, jo aso-ok iy kanuhun saba lakou handru, Malawin Mwasin asehek ili tiri lau ta Kindrei.’”
ma kado bahandra boto-on tam le ari.
Iy winiyan handru, lau mara-ei katudun nyaran.
Ano jo atou angelo ari ja edek udu loboho Rai eme loken. Ma iy tawi kalem ta Kindrei ma mulin, ma iy aloh boto-on labai ili toro angelo ma hahuw nane, Kindrei ndratehei boto-on ndra toro ta oro kabokoro-ei munyak ma ndras mara-ei.
Iy nyamun labai!
10-11 Iy angelo doh ano le badeh, iy ari in hamon tan eme len ja oloh ndrah tan. Idoh ili asahan taloh ai. Eme ma ndrau laba tinan lomadan anya tinan labai buku sun udu kandrah badeh, taku eme andri bwele-e gwa lakon ma gwa kaloh ranah ma buruwen. Nyara ndrau laba tinan nane doh badeh, iri aloh “Lakou Nyakadan.” Ya, i buku gwa doh ma tonoh (30) are bwele-e munyak mari, ronoh badeh, akohok andra-i. Gwa lakon ma gwa kaloh ranah ma buruwen doh badeh, asahan nyakadan, ma iri lau solo-an a-un gwa doh, ma nyekedei iri, ma iri mara-ei amak, tasah gwa mara-ei doh ndra nyakadan le ai.
Arile, iy angelo ndro taloh doh ili oloh ndrah tan, ma nyaro ndrah tan asahan, ma, na le liliy, iri lakou mara-ei nane Kindrei anya kamekes i san ta gok ta nadun, mara-ei kameh ano. Iri tanan mene ta gok ta Jises kameh amekes bame lewan bwe, tasah bwena mene Kindrei badeh, tone udu tiri lau mwan ma badih. Arile, udu hamon ja badeh, iy nyowaniy, ma iy atehei ili mine iri lohowan tan, iri badeh, propet tan ta asehek ili tiri lau mara-ei.
Eme ma iri lau mwan ma badih nane tana iri Kindrei bwe badeh, abo losen labai,
Ma iri ale atiye sahou tan mwasin,
Iy ndrandrei boto-on mara-ei ta nyabwe ndras nane eme bwena, iy andrei doh ta amekes iri gok tan udu madan. Iy amekes gok boto-on labai ta ariu iri mwan ma badih are kon munyak, katudun nyabwe ndras eme bwena nane. Iy mene baka ndrana ndra-in ta adai iy imek, arile ndramon ja.
Jo ale anyolom lakou ari buku ndras laba tinan, iri amekes na torowe, ma iri tubuniy hawe jih. Iri lau mene abadok sakalawi nyabwe munyak mene hawe malawin, ma sakalawi boto-on ta kane nyara ndramak nane ale, iri badeh, ales amwenen are kesehe ndras i buku torowe. Kindrei atehei iri ndran, iri aloh hap badeh, ndrala toro, ma oro tawiy udu mine oro.
boto-on marakon udu tam.
Ano angelo asehek sahou eme tek i buku doh, “Manim atur tasah handru? Jo anya kasehek tam ta nyala iy badih kede-eh ma nyala nyabwe munyak. Iy badih nane doh manyah in bwele-e nyabwe munyak, ma nyabwe munyak nane, batun ma ndro taloh ma kasoh ma ronoh udu batun. Uru lakou ma la-uh doh kameh leheya malawi iri lakou rayah, ya moso iri lakou doh badeh, aton mara-ei, arile nadah kameh jo leheyaniy mara-ei ewek tam.
eme ma Kindrei bwetenei iri kandriyen ndra-in mara-ei ta kon doh.
“Ma hawe iri lau tinan ta atondrok iri ndron mara-ei udu bolo ndras, ma iri lau ta sandroh ala ndron are kon rakon ala rakon, ma hawe iri lau nadu batun badu bolo ndras, iri mara-ei doh kameh ales are len labai ta kon tinan Babilon.
“Haleluyah!
Ya, badih tan badeh, ndranyosowani iy.
Balik badeh, ndrawendreyani iri mwan ma badih doh, eme ma Kindrei akahei iy ma buruwen ales amwenen ili bolo lek laba tinan, ta jih nyarahan labai anya udu ta bek solpa. Nyabwe munyak uru propet ta wendreya badeh, are aliy bwena; eme oro ma taloh kameh akohok sisi-in, ben, len, ben, len ta udu le buku don ai.
Kou mari ta kon tinan doh kameh asak ta udu le buku doh, winiyan bahis bwe, tasah ben kameh winiyan basahan ja bwe.
